
STEPS:

1. Put the folder "ION" somewhere and cd into it.

2. Open compile.sh and change the 
   -DGeant4_DIR=/home/souravspace/Install/GEANT4/geant4/geant4.10.05-install/lib/Geant4-10.5.1 
   to
   -DGeant4_DIR= your geant4 installation library path

3. Run the following command 

   ./compile.sh; mpic++ -o gps_gen Gps_GEN.cc; mpirun -n 4 gps_gen

   (In the command the number of cpu core can be changed from 4 to any suitable number)

    
